{"tid":552329,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[肥婆福音] 有無人試過食肉減肥法?係咪真係work?","createTime":"2018-02-06T11:51:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-06T14:10:53.000Z","uid":60219,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2c71691d7a81f1fc15b18ed89744a2a2ce2a80ae","tid":552329,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T11:51:35.000Z","msg":"食肉減肥法「阿特金斯減肥餐單」（AtkinsDiet），主張多肉低碳戒澱粉質戒糖，由於減肥不用捱餓有肉吃，曾經備受追捧，珍妮花雅麗絲頓（JenniferAniston）等荷李活女星均趨之若鶩。但食肉不吃飯不吃菜不吃水果，偏離營養均衡之道，營養學家大加批評，美國於是有醫生經研究後，將阿特金斯減肥餐單重新修訂，建議瘦身男女食肉之餘，卻不完全禁絕碳水化合物和澱粉質食物，務求做個健康減肥人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20100323/13850893\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20100323%2F13850893&d=COjGAzyZ0HpNUbDZGcisN5zN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=e2beddfd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20100323%2F13850893&h=686efd91\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20100323/13850893</a>"},{"pid":"254dff58b3af054849a601a16c53b9866ff7be15","tid":552329,"uid":107405,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T11:58:26.000Z","msg":"食肉減肥法係要戒糖 對女人黎講呢點先係問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a6fd41e75ff073538ad0db9f699d05f9004141c","tid":552329,"uid":41922,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T11:59:20.000Z","msg":"一食澱粉即刻收皮"},{"pid":"1047386f974fdd00cbc8f490fe7328a2dbbcee1b","tid":552329,"uid":36296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T11:59:28.000Z","msg":"肥婆點會忍到口唔食carbs 薯條薯片飯米線"},{"pid":"8454c549a28659cb9356bf8d74f975a8080e27c4","tid":552329,"uid":129221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T13:28:16.000Z","msg":"朋友Work呀 不過keep住唔食得/食好少 一食返就好快肥返 同佢出街要食多份薯條/飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hk